Homa Bay Governor hopeful Sammy Wakiaga has dismissed rumours that he has dropped out of the race to run for senator. He wants to run on the ODM ticket.Wakiaga accused ODM national chairman John Mbadi (pictured) of being the source of the propaganda. I want to assure you I am in the race for governor, he said. And I want to tell Mbadi to stop lies that I am vying for seats which I am not interested in. Wakiaga spoke in Sindo town after he was endorsed by Suba elders to run for governor.